summary: A cabin on the coast of Lake Ilinalta
descriptionHtml:
This is my first mod! :D

This mod adds a little cabin on the Southern coast of Lake Ilinalta (the lake North of Falkreath). To find it, go to Falkreath and take the road north to Lake Ilinalta. Once you reach the 3 way intersection at the lake, take a right and keep going until you find a big rock with a fisherwoman living on an island next to it. Once you find the fisherwoman, go South (away from the water) and keep walking around until you find the cabin. Do not cross the mountain, it\'s just next to the road! If you find silver ore while you\'re doing it, you probably found it.
author: donutzrkool
